Question: The image on the left shows a row of three red chairs next to a ladder in the bookstore.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://s3-media1.fl.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/8cozfnwh3ob-goNrAi9cMQ/348s.jpg

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many red chairs are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many red chairs are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a ladder in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a ladder in the image?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 3 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 3 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
